org.jpokemon.pmapi.pokemon.nature
Class PokemonNature

java.lang.Object
  org.jpokemon.pmapi.pokemon.nature.PokemonNature

public class PokemonNature
extends Object

Defines a nature (personality) for a Pokémon. The 25 classic natures are instantiated in the ClassicNatures class.

To define your own nature, construct an instance of this class. If you want to add attributes to the nature, it can also be extended.
